
.item-list
  %h3.item-list__title 新着アイテム
  .item-list__cards
    - @items.each do |item|
      .item-list__card
        =image_tag (item.item_images.first.image),class:"item-list__card-image"
        .item-list__card-info
          .item-list__card-info-name 
          .item-list__card-info-num
            .num__price="#{item.price}円"
            .far.fa-heart
            %p.item-list__card-info-tax (税込)
  .view-all 全ての商品をみる